00:00:00.710 --> 00:00:04.620
My name is Lauren and on behalf of Expert
Village and I'm going to talk to you about

00:00:04.620 --> 00:00:09.700
styles on the go. Another way to dress up
an easy style like this, to make it a little

00:00:09.700 --> 00:00:16.279
different from day to day is to grab a section
of hair from the nape of your neck. Especially

00:00:16.279 --> 00:00:25.079
with longer hair this will work. You separate
it, split the sections, about an inch wide.

00:00:25.079 --> 00:00:32.599
Split the sections into two. Put a little
bit of product on them, smooth them and just

00:00:32.599 --> 00:00:40.789
roll them around each other. Twist them. Depending
on how much you want your rope to be noticed

00:00:40.789 --> 00:00:44.670
you are going to make them bigger sections
or smaller sections. If I wanted this to be

00:00:44.670 --> 00:00:50.510
thicker I would grab more than that inch.
After you finished twisting you are simply

00:00:50.510 --> 00:01:06.729
going to lift it, place it over the head,
take a bobbie pin and place the bobbie pin

00:01:06.729 --> 00:01:12.909
going directly into where that teased area
is. What that's going to do is help hold this

00:01:12.909 --> 00:01:19.060
rope headband which just made it a little
fancier. And it's going to help the bobbie

00:01:19.060 --> 00:01:25.409
pin stay in from the tease. Now most people,
such as Ashleigh, her hair cannot make it

00:01:25.409 --> 00:01:31.830
to the other side. So what you would then
do is go to the other side of the nape of

00:01:31.830 --> 00:01:48.250
the neck, pull out a section, follow the same
exact protocol, smooth and rope it

00:01:48.250 --> 00:02:00.149
and then you will meet that half way through
the middle. You will lift, bring it back around,

00:02:00.149 --> 00:02:12.500
place it underneath the first rope that you
did, grab a bobbie pin and start it going

00:02:12.500 --> 00:02:21.960
backwards into the teased portion of hair
for better control. And then you can hide

00:02:21.960 --> 00:02:30.280
it underneath. As you can see it dressed up
her little do and made the hair a little bit

00:02:30.280 --> 00:02:34.360
fancier without anything and taking under
three minutes in order to do it.

